者。本书得到了联合国教科文组织的推荐，并被誉为“21世纪最伟大的人性寓言”。（泰晤士报）","price":"19.80元"},"book_id":"1041128","id":52943572},{"status":"read","rating":{"max":5,"value":"5","min":0},"updated":"2008-08-01 11:10:43","user_id":"2274326","book":{"rating":{"max":10,"numRaters":10767,"average":"8.7","min":0},"subtitle":"","author":["青山刚昌"],"pubdate":"2003-10","tags":[{"count":1449,"name":"柯南","title":"柯南"},{"count":1170,"name":"漫画","title":"漫画"},{"count":798,"name":"青山刚昌","title":"青山刚昌"},{"count":642,"name":"推理","title":"推理"},{"count":512,"name":"日本漫画","title":"日本漫画"},{"count":410,"name":"侦探","title":"侦探"},{"count":318,"name":"日本","title":"日本"},{"count":303,"name":"经典","title":"经典"}],"origin_title":"","image":"https://img3.doubanio.com\/mpic\/s1106686.jpg","binding":"平装(无盘)","translator":["natuya"],"catalog":"前情提要\nFILE.1 被隐藏的真相\nFILE.2 good-bye 茱蒂\nFILE.3 小兰的推理\nFILE.4 无法相信的结局\nFILE.5 满月之夜和黑色宴会的陷阱\nFILE.6 血染幽灵船\nFILE.7 透明人现身！\nFILE.8 工藤新一登场？！\nFILE.9 假面下的真实\nFILE.10 腐烂的苹果\nFILE.11 雨中的刻印","pages":"194","images":{"small":"https://img3.doubanio.com\/spic\/s1106686.jpg","large":"https://img3.doubanio.com\/lpic\/s1106686.jpg","medium":"https://img3.doubanio.com\/mpic\/s1106686.jpg"},"alt":"https:\/\/book.douban.com\/subject\/1138986\/","id":"1138986","publisher":"长春出版社","isbn10":"7806646086","isbn13":"9787806646083","title":"名侦探柯南42","url":"http:\/\/api.douban.com\/v2\/book\/1138986","alt_title":"","author_intro":"","summary":"在被邀请去参加幽灵船上的假面派对的小五郎和园子的面前，主办者幽灵船长被杀了！然后，为什么工藤新一会在那里现身？！另一方面，被行动可疑的茱蒂老师带走的灰原……能够阻止黑衣组织吗……怎么办，柯南……","series":{"id":"1584","title":"名侦探柯南单行本"},"price":"9.00元"},"book_id":"1138986","id":52110338},{"status":"read","rating":{"max":5,"value":"4","min":0},"updated":"2008-08-01 10:45:56","user_id":"2274326","book":{"rating":{"max":10,"numRaters":109729,"average":"8.0","min":0},"subtitle":"","author":["顾漫"],"pubdate":"2007-4","tags":[{"count":20662,"name":"顾漫","title":"顾漫"},{"count":17790,"name":"何以笙箫默","title":"何以笙箫默"},{"count":13724,"name":"小说","title":"小说"},{"count":12123,"name":"爱情","